{"tid":987023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人係尖咀海旁見過一個陸軍裝傻人？","createTime":"2019-01-19T03:43:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T13:36:58.000Z","uid":159236,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"17d4ac4d9bc6759cc3bdc6cf7a2b1b20e377f4e6","tid":987023,"uid":159236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T03:43:44.000Z","msg":"屌，同我男朋友食完飯係海旁拍下拖散下步飲下酒傾下計，原先好sweet<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n突然有個160高嘅傻佬係咁跟住我地，咁夜媽媽見佢咁慘咪傾左兩句，問佢叫咩名，佢拎張白卡出黎比我睇佢個名..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嚇撚到我急步走左，好彩男友一直攬實我，唔係實嚇死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f771f90e383e2a3ccbb5c5c070ee28d810af5652","tid":987023,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T03:44:25.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"08a078a7620fc4f099dec8557c2c23a9236eb2ce","tid":987023,"uid":159236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f771f90e383e2a3ccbb5c5c070ee28d810af5652","tid":987023,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T03:44:25.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T03:56:41.000Z","msg":"Sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n裝備好自己好快會有"},{"pid":"d4df4430889ffc124166f35500f6d94e0a9cee6b","tid":987023,"uid":159236,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T06:29:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7412e04ed495a3893021011862ba7e714ef7bacd","tid":987023,"uid":159236,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2